<cb:div type="cbeta-notes">
<head>CBETA 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0076001" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0076001">āthabbaṇo sahatthipo 此二語亦見於 Jātaka, VI, P. 490。前者註為具象之醫（Sahatthiejja），後者就五百家之象師使象之故（hatthimeṇḍa-hatthigop ka），作如是之解釋。（CBETA按：漢譯南傳大藏經此頁對應之校勘符號"[01]"與"[02]"錯置，故CBETA將此處的"[02]"校勘符號修訂成"[01]"校勘符號）</note>
<note n="0076002" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0076002">讀為 etacchattopasobhito（異本）。（CBETA按：漢譯南傳大藏經此頁對應之校勘符號"[01]"與"[02]"錯置，故CBETA將此處的"[01]"校勘符號修訂成"[02]"校勘符號）</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div type="nanchuan-notes">
<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0065001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0065001">譯為義成就。過去二十四佛之第十六佛。Buddhavaṁsa, P. 47; jātaka, I, P. 40。</note>
<note n="0067001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0067001">讀為 paricārem ahaṁ sadā（異本）。</note>
<note n="0068001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0068001">最勝水中草為最勝蓮華，即指巴多穆塔拉佛。</note>
<note n="0068002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0068002">Cela（衣）。</note>
<note n="0068003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0068003">Upacela（近衣）。</note>
<note n="0070001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0070001">manomaya-kāya 意生身，音譯摩奴末耶。此指諸佛諸阿羅漢諸天等可隨己意化出生身。周羅槃陀為意生身化作第一，或被稱為「善化形體作若干變」。</note>
<note n="0070002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0070002">兄為摩訶槃陀，弟為周羅槃陀。Jātaka I, P. 104f。</note>
<note n="0072001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0072001">向塔婆塗香泥供養。</note>
<note n="0073001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0073001">原意為充分擴展字義。</note>
<note n="0073002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0073002">Vimala（無垢）。</note>
<note n="0073003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0073003">Reṇuvatī（塵市）。</note>
<note n="0073004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0073004">Sudassana（善見）。</note>
<note n="0073005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0073005">譯為妙匠，為隨從帝釋之三十三天工巧神。</note>
<note n="0075001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0075001">Māra-savāhana 為惡魔及乘騎，依 Sutta-nipāta, V, 442之註中謂以象為乘騎。Jātaka, I, P. 71 中謂所乘乃名魔羅 Girimekhala 之象。</note>
<note n="0076001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0076001">[02]</note>
<note n="0076002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0076002">[01]</note>
<note n="0078001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0078001">為有名之無常偈，見於 D, II, P. 157。漢譯：「諸行無常，是生滅法，生滅滅己，寂滅為樂。」大般涅槃經卷下，大乘涅槃經卷十四（北本）、長阿含遊行經等皆有所出。</note>
<note n="0078002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0078002">Sapāka 四姓以下之卑賤者，此蘇巴伽長老（Sopāka）之名，亦由此而來。</note>
<note n="0079001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0079001">譯為喜見，過去二十四佛之第十三佛。Buodhavaṁsa, P. 41; Jātaka, I, P. 38。</note>
<note n="0079002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0079002">此偈之前半見於 Sutta-nipāta V. 544。</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
